    • isValidOsmTurnRestriction

      public boolean isValidOsmTurnRestriction()
      Some turn restrictions are valid in OSM but NOT valid in the graph API because the Graph API data structure is a directed graph. We use this method to filter out bad turn restrictions that are actually okay in OSM.
      Returns:
      True if the restriction relation is valid in OSM
